OL,5, Fire and electrical inspection reports 
OL,6, of an evacuated tower block have shown 
OL,7, "significant" failings in the building.
OL,9,FOn Tuesday, more than 400 residents    
OL,10,Fwere forced to leave Barton House in   
OL,11,FBristol.                               
OL,13,FA report from August shows routine     
OL,14,Fsafety checks were not carried out and 
OL,15,Ffire prevention measures were either   
OL,16,Fnot in place or built to standard.     
OL,18,FBristol City Council (BCC) said        
OL,19,Foriginal design plans were not followed
OL,20,Fduring construction in 1958.           
